Animation Properties:
  Usual:
    animation-name
    animation-duration
    animation-timing-function
    animation-delay

  Newer, Less Common:
    animation-iteration-count
    animation-fill-mode
    animation-direction
    animation-play-state

Sun Animation Excercise:
  Multiple animations,
  Transform + Colour,
  Experimentation to find the best coordinates

Shorthand:
  First value that can be parsed as time is assigned to animation-duration
  Second value that can be parsed as time is assigned to animation-delay
  All others can be put in a random order